title: List of football stadiums in the Netherlands
text: The following is a list of <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a>s in the <a href="Netherlands">Netherlands</a>, ordered by capacity. Stadiums in bold are part of the <a href="2021%E2%80%9322%20Eredivisie">2021–22 Eredivisie</a>.
